Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3, gnupg, python3-yaml, python3-watchdog, python3-filelock
Description: EncryptedSync - GPG encrypted bidirectional folder sync
 A system daemon + CLI tool to keep folders encrypted and decrypted in sync.
 Supports GPG encryption, systemd, and YAML config.
